Subject: Re: [T2] Sliding Window Glides?

VW# 281 847 723 B

Technically, VW says these only fit Mid87-91 Vanagons, but they will work
with some slight trimming and filing.  Works best when you remove the
sliding window to install.  I've done this on my 84 Westy and a friend's 76
Bus.

Around $1.50ea at VW - Special Order
